<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lamp" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lamp,</orth> 1) artificial light made with oil and a wick: <bibl n="shak. ven 755" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 755</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.98" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. III, 2, 98</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.30" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 3, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.4.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 4, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.2.20" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.4.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 4, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 3.1.63" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 1, 63</bibl>. Synonymous to torch: <cit><quote>Hymen's --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 23</bibl></cit>. Used as the emblem of life: <cit><quote>my oil-dried l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.221" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 221</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to feed for aye her l. and flames of love,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 3.2.167" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 2, 167</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>our l. is spent, it's out,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 4.15.85" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 15, 85</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) any thing shining; a) a luminary: <emph>from whom</emph> (the sun) <cit><quote>each l. and shining star doth borrow,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 861" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 861</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. aww 2.1.167" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 1, 167</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.1.31" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 1, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.4.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 4, 7</bibl>. b) the eye: <cit><quote>four such --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 489" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 489</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ven 489" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 489</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 5.315" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 315</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 5, 8</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>